title: Ebro In The Morning - Deja Vu! DaBaby & Dave Chappelle Controversies + Valentine's Day Plans
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 2/10/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez, and the crew are in the studio talking about Valentine's Day Plans (16), recent celebrity leaks (39), both DaBaby and Dave Chappelle's new drama (24), and backlash against harm reduction programs (1). 

Get excited for our new segment Black Facts and the also the gurus help solve your problems. All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
